{"tid":1756881,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[做功能組別選民其實無你想像中咁難]","createTime":"2019-11-26T08:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T02:07:10.000Z","uid":289611,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"7e728851a27f03cd1fde0a53fd0bdc9648108c66","tid":1756881,"uid":289611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"[做功能組別選民其實無你想像中咁難]<br />\n<br />\n麻煩如果以下係你職業界別，花少少時間睇兩頁紙睇下你係咪有資格做功能界別選民？<br />\n(<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/gn-full_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Fgn-full_c.pdf&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=e9b07991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/gn-full_c.pdf</a>)<br />\n<br />\n*會計界, 建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界, 飲食界, 教育界, 工程界, 金融界, 金融服務界, 衞生服務界, 進出口界, 資訊科技界. 保險界, 勞工界, 法律界, 醫學界. 地產及建造界, 社會福利界. 體育、演藝、文化及出版界, 紡織及製衣界, 旅遊界, 航運交通界, 批發及零售界, 中醫界 *<br />\n<br />\n如果係，麻煩花少少時間填呢份表交返就可以啦！<br />\n(<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV04R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=c05feb1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf)<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 仲有拜託2020年9月6, 13, 20星期日盡量唔好外遊<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳"},{"pid":"6e43508f0074b8147e7e1fee11821a748a17bb01","tid":1756881,"uid":289611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:48:41.000Z","msg":"P仔推唔到"},{"pid":"790ae79712dc2be3574822013ae264ed807d782b","tid":1756881,"uid":289611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:49:44.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫推"},{"pid":"fe04f066a4f26c5cec23aac92d5b63e6a85acb10","tid":1756881,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:50:12.000Z","msg":"值得推<br />\n但咁擺兩個page出黎應該無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3070fe9ce79667b8577770b0c30dfe642396fb0e"